      • getInputDatasets

        public Map<String,TableModel> getInputDatasets()
        Description copied from interface: ScapeData
        Return a map of tables which will be displayed in the Navigator under the "Datasets" node. These can be any data the simulation wants to display in tabulated form, that does not change after loading. The map key is the name used for the table in the Navigator.
        Specified by:
        getInputDatasets in interface ScapeData
        Returns:
        map of tables for display.

      • getParameterSets

        public Map<String,ParameterSet> getParameterSets()
        Description copied from interface: ScapeData
        Return a map of tables which will be displayed in the Navigator under the "Parameter Set" node. These can be any data the simulation wants to make available as parameters for manipulation by the user. The map key is the name used for the table in the Navigator.
        Specified by:
